  "title": "Group Fitness Instructor (Part Time/Full Time welcome)",
  "description": "<p>Ready to be part of a fun/exciting community? As a Group Fitness Instructor, you will lead and instruct group fitness classes, create engaging workouts, motivate participants, and ensure a safe and inclusive environment for all members.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Click Apply if you are: </strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>A genuine passion for fitness and helping others achieve their goals</li>\n  <li>Certification in group fitness instruction or relevant fitness certification</li>\n  <li>Strong interpersonal and communication skills</li>\n  <li>Ability to create a motivating and inclusive fitness environment</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of safe and effective exercise techniques</li>\n  <li>Experience in leading group fitness classes</li>\n</ul>",
